	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Grand Theftendo is optimized for MMC5, if a Squeedo version was possible it would look very different, and would have to be re-written in a huge way.
<br />
<br />MMC5 is totally nuts, it enhances the PPU's capabilities (more tiles without coding tricks and higher color resolution).  Squeedo is fairly passive with the PPU, like most mappers are.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


